name: VOID (itch) (Rediska_235)
description:
Description 

VOID is a maze platformer game created for Mini Jam 67: Void. 

The game is still in development.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Controls

A or Left Arrow - Move Left D or Right Arrow - Move Right Space - Jump F - Put the lantern E - Go to the next level

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Have a nice game  ; )
